{"tid":1844610,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"拜年先知有荷蘭血統　唐詩詠：不要再問個鼻點解咁高","createTime":"2020-01-26T17:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T17:17:56.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c007debd8d62d2d6ce11921a608c5fd9c1080f4d","tid":1844610,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T17:05:13.000Z","msg":"大年初一不少人都會到親友家拜年，唐詩詠就在社交網中，分享了一件拜年趣事！她發文說新年最美好的一件事就是與親戚好友敍舊聊天，而且會在交談當中「發現好多嘢」，她說親戚覺得自己「個鼻最似爸爸」，她反問：「爸爸又唔係鬼佬點解個鼻會咁高？」<br />\n<img src=\"https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/6789df2dgy1gb9dhavidpj20cx0gcwfh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx1.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F6789df2dgy1gb9dhavidpj20cx0gcwfh.jpg&h=684bc100&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/6789df2dgy1gb9dhavlv4j20lz0g576m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx1.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F6789df2dgy1gb9dhavlv4j20lz0g576m.jpg&h=eae522a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/6731c01ely1gb7um0psk3j20pr0q4q69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx3.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F6731c01ely1gb7um0psk3j20pr0q4q69.jpg&h=2c23380e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/6731c01egy1gb5s6hjgacj23402c01kz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx4.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F6731c01egy1gb5s6hjgacj23402c01kz.jpg&h=d5848309&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/6731c01egy1gb5s6ful7nj21e011iqkx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx4.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F6731c01egy1gb5s6ful7nj21e011iqkx.jpg&h=77643c80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n親戚終於解開謎團：「你嫲嫲係荷蘭加印尼，你個鼻實高㗎喎！」唐詩詠知道後說：「唔係啩，我係福建加印尼加荷蘭混血。」她父親就「扯開話題」：「乜你唔知嘅咩？ 我冇講咩，唔係好記得，食咩甜品？我要合桃露。」解開身世之謎後，她亦打趣道：「唔好再問我個鼻點解咁高」、「因為我有荷蘭鼻」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/6731c01ely1gb57zxgjqtj20u00njtbg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx4.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F6731c01ely1gb57zxgjqtj20u00njtbg.jpg&h=83a3cc38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/6731c01egy3gax4jdk4i8j20u40k2qr6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx1.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F6731c01egy3gax4jdk4i8j20u40k2qr6.jpg&h=1bd89a4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/6731c01egy1gax40l35ogj20l40l4q4y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx3.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F6731c01egy1gax40l35ogj20l40l4q4y.jpg&h=eee71443&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/6731c01ely1gau8ptb7i4j20u00k040y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx2.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F6731c01ely1gau8ptb7i4j20u00k040y.jpg&h=0bcadeea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/6731c01ely1gain058z0kj20u011i7a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx2.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F6731c01ely1gain058z0kj20u011i7a3.jpg&h=4806bd45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/6731c01ely1ga9d5hharkj20u011hk0x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx3.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F6731c01ely1ga9d5hharkj20u011hk0x.jpg&h=ddc2c2f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/6731c01egy3ga0vdmfqr9j20qo0zkh6o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx4.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F6731c01egy3ga0vdmfqr9j20qo0zkh6o.jpg&h=e5167ea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://sina.com.hk/news/article/20200126/0/0/53/-11118788.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20200126%2F0%2F0%2F53%2F-11118788.html&d=0fPPgjUU32Qc%2B%2Bj2t4ropPrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=320091a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://sina.com.hk/news/article/20200126/0/0/53/-11118788.html</a>"},{"pid":"bda831ad57f64e73790de0f5675b78748bfca5a5","tid":1844610,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci